description: The demonic soldiers of Leviathan fight on as The Devil's Brigade saga continues, with The Matrix's Larry Wachowski bringing you the next chapter in "Endolsung: The Final Solution." The Cenobites have set gears into motion to bring unspeakable horrors to Earth, and it seems as if no one can stand in their way. HELLRAISER MASTERPIECES continues to bring back the best of the classic, epic series, a must-read for any fan of Clive Barker's twisted creations!
name: Devil's Brigade, Part 12: Enoolsung: The Final Solution; Mazes of the Mind

description: The EPIC BATTLE that has been building since SPAWN's milestone 200th issue is here: SPAWN vs. MALEBOLGIA! What happens in these pages will change Jim forever. Prepare to witness the beginning of a NEW EVOLUTION!
name: The Gathering Storm, Part 6 (of 6)

The Beautiful Princess refuses to kiss the frog and calls on Pater to save her from the Pink Panther and Creepy Frog, and Pater has been wanting a Pink Panther head to mount in his trophy room.
